  "content": "property which is an observable that emits an array of target definitions. The `workspaceId` property is also bound, as well as several other properties that configure the component's behavior and appearance.\n```csharp\n<div\n  class=\"portfolio-exposures-container pm-ui-combined-grid-container__splitter-horizontal\"\n  slot=\"1\"\n>\n  <div *ngIf=\"showTemplate$ | async\">\n    <pm-ui-widget>\n      <pm-ui-widget-header pmUiWidgetHeader></pm-ui-widget-header>\n      <div class=\"portfolio-exposures-placeholder\" pmUiWidgetContent>\n        To view one or more targets against a portfolio, select and load from the subscribed\n        targets on top.\n      </div>\n    </pm-ui-widget>\n  </div>\n  <div *ngIf=\"!(showTemplate$ | async)\" class=\"portfolio-target-filter\">\n    <span>\n      <pm-ui-view-filter\n        data-cy=\"pm-ui-portfolio-target-view-filter\"\n        moduleId=\"portfolio-target-details-view-filter\"\n        [workspaceId]=\"workspaceId\"\n        [isFaceted]=\"true\"\n        [subscribeToUpdates]=\"true\"\n        (valuesChanged)=\"onValuesChanged($event)\"\n      ></pm-ui-view-filter>\n    </span>\n    <span class=\"aggregation-checkbox\">\n      <aux-checkbox\n        data-cy=\"aggregation-checkbox\"\n        [label]=\"'Show Target Level Aggregation'\"\n        [isChecked]=\"false\"\n        [disabled]=\"!(showTemplate$ | async)\"\n        (checkboxChanged)=\"onTargetLevelAggregationEnabled($event)\"\n      ></aux-checkbox\n    ></span>\n  </div>\n  <pm-ui-portfolio-exposures\n    *ngIf=\"!(showTemplate$ | async)\"\n    data-cy=\"pm-ui-portfolio-target-content-exposure\"\n    name=\"Portfolio Exposures\"\n    [workspaceId]=\"workspaceId\"\n    moduleId=\"portfolio-details-multi-target\"\n    [showTargetName]=\"true\"\n    [showActiveExposuresOnly]=\"portfolioDetailsStoreService.showActiveExposuresOnly$ | async\"\n    [highlightingThreshold]=\"portfolioDetailsStoreService.highlightingThreshold$ | async\"\n    [selectedPortfolios]=\"selectedSubscriptionPortfolio\"\n    [allSubscribedPortfolios]=\"selectedPortfolios\"\n    [targetDefinitions]=\"targetDetailList$ | async\"\n    [childTargetDefinitions]=\"targetDetailsOverrideMap\"\n    [activeExposureSelection]=\"activeExposureSelection$ | async\"\n    [processPositionUpdateOnPortfolioSelectionChange]=\"false\"\n    (selectedActiveExposures)=\"onActiveExposuresSelected($event)\"\n    (selectedRows)=\"onSelectedTargetDefinitions($event)\"\n    (editedExposureRows)=\"onEditedExposureRows($event)\"\n  ></pm-ui-portfolio-exposures>\n</div>\n```\nThis is another custom component `pm-ui-portfolio-exposures` that displays portfolio exposures for one or more targets. The component is bound to several properties, including the `workspaceId`, `targetDetailList$`, `selectedSubscriptionPortfolio`, and `activeExposureSelection$` observables. The component also emits events when the user interacts with it, such as selecting active exposures, selecting rows, or editing exposure rows.\n```python\n<div class=\"footer\">\n  <div class=\"actions-container\">\n    <p class=\"footer-text\">Targets {{ targetsStatus }}</p>\n    <aux-button\n      class=\"footer-left-item\"\n      type=\"secondary\"\n      label=\"Save Changes\"\n      data-cy=\"pm-ui-portfolio-targets-save-changes-button\"\n      (click)=\"onSaveChangesClicked()\"\n      [isDisabled]=\"disableSaveChanges\"\n    ></aux-button>\n    <aux-button\n      class=\"footer-left-item\"\n      type=\"secondary\"\n```",
